      "content": "it's not just the timing. now that i'm in this office, i've noticed they've given me all this new tech—a \"specialized\" secure phone and a laptop that's managed by a completely different IT team than the rest of the floor. they say it's for \"executive privacy,\" but it feels more like they're just making it easier to track every single thing i do. do you think they're trying to box me in?",
